A string used to define the absolute URL of your app. This includes the protocol, for example {{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK https://example.com }}{\fldrslt{https://example.com\ul0\cf0}}}}\f0\fs22 . No paths allowed, only protocol, domain and (optionally) port.\par
